33:03.380 --> 33:06.820
Down at t'bus stop in Selby
Bridge. I always liked him.

33:11.260 --> 33:13.500
Shall we get a takeaway tonight?

33:48.220 --> 33:51.020
- I thought I was
going to be late. - No.

33:52.220 --> 33:54.980
- Is that...? - Only
