36:00.740 --> 36:04.780
- We can still be friends.
- Sure. - Can't we? - Sure.

36:36.900 --> 36:38.100
Hello, love.

36:41.180 --> 36:43.060
Can I stop here for a bit?

36:48.260 --> 36:51.140
Um... Yeah, course you can.

36:53.580 --> 36:56.050
- What's happened?
