37:43.580 --> 37:47.900
Ever since Daisy were born, she's
been off her... flaming trolley.

37:49.140 --> 37:53.170
- And now, she's just gone
completely fruit loop. - What's up?

37:53.220 --> 37:58.050
Daniel's going to be sleeping on
