37:58.100 --> 38:01.300
- Hiya.
- Hiya.

38:06.460 --> 38:07.940
Do you want another one?

38:10.740 --> 38:12.020
No.

38:13.220 --> 38:14.740
No...

38:17.980 --> 38:20.410
No, I ought to be getting off home.

38:20.460 --> 38:22.340
You all right, John?

38:24.860 --> 38:27.340
