39:00.820 --> 39:02.890
Let's just get you into your car.

39:02.940 --> 39:04.810
Oh, God, I don't think...

39:04.860 --> 39:09.290
- Oh... I don't think I can drive.
- I can drive.

39:09.340 --> 39:12.530
- What's happening to me?
- Just...

39:12.580 --> 39:15.010
Where's your keys?

39:15.060 --> 39:17.100
- Whoa...
- Whoa! OK.

41:05.900 --> 41:08.900
- Morning. Want to...?
- No, no, please.

41:13.820 --> 41:15.610
Following the meeting I had yesterday

41:15.660 --> 41:17.050
with the Assistant Chief Con

41:17.100 --> 41:19.170
and the SIOs in the
other two investigations,

41:19.220 --> 41:23.050
it's been concluded that there
is sufficient evidence, well...

41:23.100 --> 41:26.050
more than sufficient evidence,
to link this operation

41:26.100 --> 41:29.650
with Operation Sycamore
and Operation Livingston.

41:29.700 --> 41:31.010
The upshot, therefore,

41:31.060 --> 41:34.090
